    <description><![CDATA[1.安装arch-install-scripts paru -S arch-install-scripts 2.启用支持 sudo nvim /etc/lxc/default.conf lxc.idmap = u 0 100000 65536 lxc.idmap = g 0 100000 65536 3重新映射用户和组 sudo nvim /etc/subuid root:10000]]></description>
